snippet.title: VOTE!!! The Game Review [iPhone & iPad]
snippet.description:
This is an unbiased video review of Vote The Game for the iOS platform (iPhone, iPad & iPod Touch). This mobile game was developed & published by Chair Entertainment Group (http://epicgames.com/about/).  Vote The Game is political satire at it's finest as Obama & Romney Face Off in an "Infinity Blade like" brawler for iOS.

Purchase Vote The Game in the iTunes app store for FREE:
http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/vote!!!/id534309109?ls=1&mt=8
 
The review was produced by Tony from the Classic L337 Gaming & Electronic Podcast.
 
Check out our podcast at http://www.classicL337.com
 
Outro Video Produced by BMZLoop http://www.youtube.com/bmzloop
Outro Music Produced by Richie Branson: http://richiebranson.com/
